column16: Michael Wacha singles on a ground ball to shortstop Starlin Castro, deflected by pitcher Donn Roach.   Xavier Scruggs to 3rd.    Peter Bourjos to 2nd.
Peter Bourjos singles on a ground ball to center fielder Dexter Fowler.   Xavier Scruggs to 2nd.
Xavier Scruggs singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Dexter Fowler.   Yadier Molina scores.
Randal Grichuk flies out to center fielder Dexter Fowler.
Yadier Molina doubles (13) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Dexter Fowler.   Jason Heyward scores.
Jason Heyward singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Dexter Fowler.
Matt Carpenter grounds out, second baseman Addison Russell to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.
Kolten Wong flies out to center fielder Dexter Fowler.
Michael Wacha grounds out, shortstop Starlin Castro to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.
Peter Bourjos grounds into a force out, shortstop Starlin Castro to second baseman Addison Russell.   Randal Grichuk out at 2nd.    Peter Bourjos to 1st.
Xavier Scruggs lines out to second baseman Addison Russell.
Yadier Molina grounds into a double play, third baseman Kris Bryant to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.   Jhonny Peralta out at 3rd.
Jason Heyward singles on a sharp ground ball to right fielder Mike Baxter.   Matt Carpenter to 3rd.    Jhonny Peralta to 2nd.
Jhonny Peralta singles on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Chris Coghlan.   Matt Carpenter to 2nd.
Matt Carpenter grounds into a force out, first baseman Anthony Rizzo to shortstop Starlin Castro.   Kolten Wong out at 2nd.    Matt Carpenter to 1st.
Kolten Wong singles on a ground ball to second baseman Addison Russell.
